{"tid":937853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又係支那人］𠝹褲黨再現 休班車長褲袋遭𠝹爛險被偷銀包","createTime":"2018-12-12T00:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T01:43:53.000Z","uid":28435,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b75b562b265e3f13800ecb54b44f535f99bcf6c2","tid":937853,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T00:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FF0h4z9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFF0h4z9.png&h=ec192cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴士𠝹褲黨再現！下午2時許，58歲姓李的休班城巴車長乘坐8P路線新巴前往小西灣，其間他坐在上層小睡片刻，至巴士駛經東區走廊近鰂魚涌公園時，他感覺遭人碰撞，於是立即起身，赫見左邊褲袋有被𠝹爛的痕迹，懷疑坐在旁邊的男乘客企圖偷銀包，遂即作出指摘。男乘客初時操不純正廣東話反駁，未幾突然衝落下層企圖落車，李見狀立即尾隨並通知車長報警，下層乘客亦立即出手，合力將男乘客制服。<br />\n<br />\n巴士其後在柴灣公園對開的巴士站停下，警方到場調查，並於樓梯位置撿獲數塊刀片，懷疑與案有關，隨即拘捕該名男乘客，而涉事的城巴車長亦無損失。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，下午2時52分接獲報案，指一名巴士職員乘搭巴士期間，被人用𠝹刀𠝹爛左邊褲袋，企圖偷竊財物。警方接報到場調查，於巴士梯間附近撿獲3塊刀片，並拘捕一名50歲姓曹的內地男子，涉嫌企圖盜竊及外出時備有偷竊用的物品，案件交由東區警區刑事調查隊第一隊跟進。"},{"pid":"859fe4b416e8e2f18191e0e7aac2645a20ef521b","tid":937853,"uid":5603,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T00:19:13.000Z","msg":"輸入專才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fb992c1b16c07fd6e610cb4f98044028d38681","tid":937853,"uid":219515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T00:19:48.000Z","msg":"我呢名書記睇黎要為香港區治安做下野先至得啦"},{"pid":"a3c242680a5de65745397c25212b6935dd6a8365","tid":937853,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T00:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341d3c83b32f3709e1b6fb155f521090a00e6e91","tid":937853,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T00:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 專材"},{"pid":"da5a198c9ba469c8f1fb3fe14c27f0f023fe6b5e","tid":937853,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T00:36:32.000Z","msg":"呢d支那人，打佢一身就啱"},{"pid":"1af9c2fb629b4c077ea9a6f4c6559d695a0ba6d5","tid":937853,"uid":167186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T00:38:23.000Z","msg":"支那人永遠都無一個係無辜"},{"pid":"2106dda07041a4e9f38ee9905e11c975cf15a20f","tid":937853,"uid":48011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T01:36:50.000Z","msg":"97之前果班手腳乾淨利落好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746b6c0f27db84b5f7a8931cd0fd90f94d4e7405","tid":937853,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T01:37:40.000Z","msg":"發現不純正廣東話男子有香港身份證住新公屋拎緊綜援"},{"pid":"be772f526e090398475829429dc34e7af2d2ba1e","tid":937853,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2106dda07041a4e9f38ee9905e11c975cf15a20f","tid":937853,"uid":48011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T01:36:50.000Z","msg":"97之前果班手腳乾淨利落好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T01:43:53.000Z","msg":"拎埋AK添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}